      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: The letter is addressed to \"the commander, my master, lord and sir\" (ll. 2-3). The sender seems to be the addressee's agent who went to inspect the latter's estate about which he reports in the present letter (l. 2-3; l. 4).\nVerso: One line with a name, probably belonging to the address of the letter."
